{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/employment/hygienic-measures-workplace","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Hygienic measures in the workplace","meta_description":"Hygienic rules and recommendations for work in the workplace.","content":{"processed":"<h2>Rules and recommendations</h2>\n<p>The workplace is one of the <strong>most</strong> common places of <strong>infection</strong>, as there is a significant concentration of people from many different areas, who stay there for a long period of time. Therefore, it is <strong>necessary to follow increased hygienic measures</strong>.</p>\n<p>Keep a <strong>distance of 2 meters</strong> from other people and <strong>wash or disinfect your hands regularly</strong>. There is also an <strong>obligation to wear a face mask at the workplace</strong>. See the Face Masks section under the subject <a href=\"/en/situations/face-masks/workplace\" rel=\"nofollow\">Workplace</a> for more information on the obligation to wear a mask in the workplace.</p>\n<p><strong>Ventilate</strong> the interior space of the workplace regularly.</p>\n<p>The <strong>employer is obliged to provide disinfectants</strong> and place them near frequently touched objects. It is also necessary to frequently disinfect these areas, such as the handles, railings, shopping carts, elevators, tables, etc.</p>\n<p>In grocery stores, the operator is obliged to provide the customers with disposable gloves or tools possibly used for hands in a similar way (e.g. plastic bags) — free of charge. They must also provide sufficient protective equipment for their employees.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/hygienic-measures-workplace"},"changed":"2020-12-02T15:24:55+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-06T09:32:10+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3Dx9NOUr0ItNA","title":"Covid-19 spread on workplace and how to stop it"},{"uri":"https://koronavirus.mzcr.cz/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Př%C3%ADprava-pracoviště-na-covid-19_12052020.pdf","title":"Detailed information about hygiene prevention (in Czech)"}],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia","drupal_internal__tid":"33"}],"icon":{"code":"work"},"situation_type":{"name":"Employment","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"work"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"What is the purpose of face masks and respirators?","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks-and-respirators/what-purpose-face-masks-and-respirators","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Infected colleague","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/infected-colleague","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Employer/Employee relations","path":{"alias":"/situations/tracing-and-testing-faq/employeremployee-relations","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Hand washing","path":{"alias":"/situations/hygiene/hand-washing","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":null,"last_updated":"2020-12-02T15:49:01+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Employment","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"work"},"situation":[{"id":"3872e0d0-90c3-5b68-b0c4-03987ad099d1","title":"Home office","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/home-office"}},{"id":"309c223d-2475-58de-bf5d-298398cad794","title":"Hygienic measures in the workplace","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/hygienic-measures-workplace"}},{"id":"a7f20be3-3a34-58b7-9714-45a043c46f27","title":"eNeschopenka","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/eneschopenka"}},{"id":"8222ed2e-b8bd-5f5f-afc7-3d366af361ac","title":"Wage compensation","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/wage-compensation"}},{"id":"8c196506-f43f-5b68-99a1-585972e45b75","title":"Job interviews","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/job-interviews"}},{"id":"53f19155-d696-553a-8feb-d83685c899b5","title":"The protection of employees","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/protection-employees"}},{"id":"55d2f5